    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sad Ghouls </h2>is a singleplayer arcade survival shooter, where endless hordes of ghouls constantly stream into the arena.<br>Kill enemies to score points and increment the combo counter. Getting higher combo means better weapons and sometimes new weapons.<br>All score from kills gets multiplied by the combo counter. Choosing a higher difficulty setting results in tougher enemies that grant higher score. But a chill player can choose an easier difficulty to chill and still have a chance to appear on the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/5901d0945bc3e9e3a5fef55322d3936f.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/5901d0945bc3e9e3a5fef55322d3936f.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/5901d0945bc3e9e3a5fef55322d3936f.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Select weapons, level and options that change the flow of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Humble beginnings</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/0b7044abe210c3f4086cd96c9e7f288e.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/0b7044abe210c3f4086cd96c9e7f288e.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/0b7044abe210c3f4086cd96c9e7f288e.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Start small with weak weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level up</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/808e7fd5b3ae93227ddbffd73b737bdf.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/808e7fd5b3ae93227ddbffd73b737bdf.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/808e7fd5b3ae93227ddbffd73b737bdf.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kill ghouls to level up your weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obliterate the ghouls</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/ad6898bccd02dd05f11cfd46fe7391bd.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/ad6898bccd02dd05f11cfd46fe7391bd.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/ad6898bccd02dd05f11cfd46fe7391bd.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use powerful weapons to destroy the opposition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't get overrun</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/f5ad41264256d292c032c021dbc41520.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/f5ad41264256d292c032c021dbc41520.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/f5ad41264256d292c032c021dbc41520.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>No time to rest, enemies get stronger over time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Global leaderboards</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/fd005d0cfd0608bade097208885dd568.poster.avif?t=1746829552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/fd005d0cfd0608bade097208885dd568.webm?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884850/extras/fd005d0cfd0608bade097208885dd568.mp4?t=1746829552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>View leaderboards and compete with friends and strangers.<br>Top 10 players on the leaderboard get a chance for a wizard with their name to visit other players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special waves</h2>Experience special frenzy, devil and wizard waves.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8 different weapons<br></li><li>3 differnet enemies<br></li><li>4 different maps<br></li><li>4 difficulties<br></li><li> Global leaderboards<br></li><li> 11+ steam achievements<br></li><li> and many more planned features....</li></ul><br>Contributions can be found in the community hub.",
